    "Lastly, when we considered the type of ML algorithm, we found that string representation was the most common choice for traditional ML algorithms, while visual encoding was the most common format for neural networks, followed closely by time series data.",
    "We focused on features directly related to scanpaths, fixations, saccades, or AOIs for feature engineering.",
